metadata.name: The Mystery Inside Me
metadata.description:
★ In addition to the first collector of the «Dreamtime» collection!


The poem «The Mystery Inside Me» by @saitlait

Your eyes sparkle, but it's not for me.
Your lips whisper everything, but it's not for me.
Your hand on the table, but it's not for me.
You leave everything behind, but it's not for me.
